Business Brief -- Unilever N.V.:
   Pretax $35 Million Charge
   Taken in Fourth Quarter
The Chesebrough program will involve offering certain of
the unit's 3,400 employees voluntary early retirements.
Unilever said it may also follow up with layoffs if
necessary. Chesebrough-Ponds has annual sales of about $1
billion; parent Unilever has $40 billion in sales.